---
title: Cheesy Alfredo Style Prawn Linguine with spinach, chives and balsamic glaze
description: Our take on the famous pasta dish conceived in 1908 by Alfredo di Lelio, an Italian restaurateur. This is a creamy cheesy recipe sprinkled with chives and filled with juicy prawns.
